node.title: TikTok celebrity cosmetic surgeon banned from performing surgery
node.description: A senior associate of the controversial clinic owner Dr Daniel Lanzer has been banned by the national health regulator from performing all types of cosmetic surgery and ordered to remove his social media posts.

node.title: South Africa's president calls for lifting of Omicron travel bans
node.description: South Africa's president has condemned travel bans enacted against his country and its neighbours over the new coronavirus variant Omicron.
